Changelog

dirvacua-0.0.6

 * Added an example dummy nose test.
 * Made a single place for storing version number.

dirvacua-0.0.5

 * Bug fix: recursive option now processes the target directory.

dirvacua-0.0.4

 * Added processing for directories and files.
 * Added '-v' and '-q' short forms of  '--verbose' and '--quiet'.

dirvacua-0.0.3

 * Deleted legacy code.
 * Removed copy N paste error in setup.py
 * Improved documentation (spelling and markup errors).
